      "sc:citation": {
        "@id": "https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0174744"
      },
      "sc:description": "This is a Hi-C analysis package using a cumulative binomial test to detect interactions between distal genomic loci that have significantly more reads than expected by chance in Hi-C experiments. It takes mapped paired NGS reads as input and gives back the list of significant interactions for a given bin size in the genome.",
